{"tid":1085027,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"固姑古愈多 麻雀就愈少","createTime":"2019-03-30T23:13:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T19:06:22.000Z","uid":177089,"like":101,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"356bbb4d59550df15f5dbdbf3956da49d2a22392","tid":1085027,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T23:13:53.000Z","msg":"唔知你地有無留意 最近幾年條街少咗好多麻雀<br />\n以前見到一群群麻雀飛嚟飛去 <br />\n依家條街就得返一堆固姑古鳩叫<br />\n<br />\n有個成語叫雀巢鳩佔 啲斑鳩似住自己大隻啲<br />\n飛去麻雀個巢度趕走人 推走人啲蛋 然後生蛋 <br />\n<br />\n一開始飛咗一班固姑古 就會愈嚟愈多<br />\n麻雀最後連生蛋嘅地方都無 就愈嚟愈少<br />\n<br />\n但其實 固姑古本身唔係嚟自香港㗎喎<br />\n灰斑鳩在中國相當常見，指名亞種（S. d. decaocto）分佈於華北和四川，亞種S. d. stoliczkae分佈於新疆喀什和天山地區，亞種S. d. xanthocyclus作為迷鳥偶然出現在安徽、福建福州和雲南。<br />\n<br />\n哦原來係大陸嚟嘅 但當你話 咁多固姑古 點解唔捉佢地限制數量<br />\n但原來根據野生動物保護條例 市民係無權咁做 <br />\n保護巢及蛋<br />\n任何人除按照特別許可證行事外，不得取去、移走、損害、銷毀或故意干擾任何受保護野生動物的巢或蛋。<br />\n<br />\n但呢種入侵物種 政府點解唔做野 保護返麻雀嘅生存空間？ <br />\n<br />\n珠頸斑鳩有兩個亞種。指名亞種（S. c. chinensis）分佈於中國華中至華南大部分地區<br />\n唔好意思啊 佢地已經做咗本地居民 依家係本地種嚟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LoxHd0K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLoxHd0K.png&h=a6eb60b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n包容下啦麻雀 橫掂你好快住都無得住㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba22510ea8ef5dc7d3935ded2a44ab627a0deabc","tid":1085027,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T23:15:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8db8f58d93443134cf6a277f1ef8aec0c5b2d2b","tid":1085027,"uid":24759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T23:27:42.000Z","msg":"麻雀冇咩留意，但白鴿就多咗好多"},{"pid":"f4b62a25c423660454e6709c8948249f939e7563","tid":1085027,"uid":201949,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T23:29:40.000Z","msg":"有弦外之音喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e661d02c783b795c19671c582bd9bd8a771bb27","tid":1085027,"uid":245126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T23:29:44.000Z","msg":"我係麻雀仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dcd0445e5007d04524b05e51cdb2f508c913adc","tid":1085027,"uid":150750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T23:37:16.000Z","msg":"好撚憎啲固姑古<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f88e41d341634c62ea4648a5c02d88fc3a1213b","tid":1085027,"uid":132326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T23:38:42.000Z","msg":"麻雀好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"323fd9e634dbcafcdc40df2d611a2891e5b65a42","tid":1085027,"uid":177089,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T23:48:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qDdSBqE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqDdSBqE.png&h=f4953518&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"442a6b58c575e14e7e908b7d7f09147b40afecde","tid":1085027,"uid":46170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T23:49:56.000Z","msg":"餵多d麻雀食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65a057f2893339721090d6084f873dfb7670075a","tid":1085027,"uid":177089,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T23:50:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AAr5OHU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAAr5OHU.gif&h=06b0939c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f2715f6ddcf52b25af2b5f55eb9111c97c99c40","tid":1085027,"uid":177089,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T23:55:35.000Z","msg":"走在街上，你有無發現麻雀少了？全港麻雀普查調查結果發現，今年全麻雀數量較前年少逾兩成，由32萬隻減至25萬隻，是自有紀錄以來新低。香港觀鳥會指，情況值得關注，估計因今年首5個月雨量極少，乾旱天氣令麻雀延遲繁殖和離巢，亦減少食物令麻雀難以生存。<br />\n<br />\n全港麻雀普查今年（2018)5月進行，透過260名普查員在全港78條路線，以樣線調查方式收集數據，每條路線長約1公里，共記錄3,843隻麻雀，估算全港有約25.2萬隻麻雀，較前年32.3萬隻少約22%，創三年新低。而78條普查路線中，7成路線所錄得的麻雀數量均比過去兩年少。"},{"pid":"fa64f8860610ec7e9c4c1851088bbf7757beb7f9","tid":1085027,"uid":177089,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T00:49:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6qeRSjx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6qeRSjx.png&h=68add56c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f0a435ae0c32d2a8fdf74ca7202ac2b7e2de26e","tid":1085027,"uid":33174,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T02:14:16.000Z","msg":"政府幫緊班鳩上樓 <br />\n目的係大換血 將啲麻雀趕走<br />\n中央政策黎"},{"pid":"593037893cc805ecdc8e8415141fad8a993254c4","tid":1085027,"uid":101110,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T02:52:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PZUuEEZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPZUuEEZ.png&h=3f209003&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n明明麻雀靚固姑古噉多<br />\n一見到固姑古條死人頸就想嘔吐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29c16df54f3ddc7f1d163435e241211142fbf0f9","tid":1085027,"uid":167566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T02:53:47.000Z","msg":"Nothing can do ar"},{"pid":"613a61327e69ce4b152b46fc19b17c823a973424","tid":1085027,"uid":177089,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T03:06:27.000Z","msg":"麻雀天生唔夠固姑古打 政府同你講不干預係自由政策"},{"pid":"714af9afa9b928a33cdb0e9690c7d8aad95826bf","tid":1085027,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T03:09:06.000Z","msg":"以前一對麻雀見到有一隻固姑古飛埋去搶食<br />\n依家見到一堆固姑古 麻雀就得返一兩隻四圍匿"},{"pid":"824aea2b149aa86e049bc38f68b86ad0a6045452","tid":1085027,"uid":206812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T03:16:14.000Z","msg":"唔講唔覺 而家真係好少見到麻雀仔"},{"pid":"b91226a08da6fed6184fe3fd4da64742ac841a1e","tid":1085027,"uid":14083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T03:18:42.000Z","msg":"麻雀好可愛，細過救過一隻 麻雀bb"},{"pid":"9e915e6767e26d11b8e17250a6f5fde1608a8f52","tid":1085027,"uid":88428,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T03:22:04.000Z","msg":"好想搵bb彈射死d鴿<br />\n又肥又醜好撚污糟成地屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74e390635b9006a4fb11898bd168330034f9386a","tid":1085027,"uid":117422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T03:23:07.000Z","msg":"固姑古超仆街 成日捕係冷氣機<br />\n開冷氣趕完第二日同樣時間又出現<br />\n兩隻一齊啤住你吹咩嘅樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef8387ab19c6e958bfab59e8ccd19544d85cd28b","tid":1085027,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T03:37:49.000Z","msg":"支那人不嬲最憎保護佢地既生物<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/打麻雀运动\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E6%89%93%E9%BA%BB%E9%9B%80%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%A8&d=Sk6y7wLkZ8LsH37jlkaP97%2F5csivkdzoxKq11rtKUO4%3D&h=d8e80234\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/打麻雀运动</a><br />\n毛澤東根據當時情況綜合判斷，後在中共會議上全體討論認為麻雀以穀物為食，影響到農業生產，因而將麻雀定為四害之中的老四，在中國開展了的除四害運動"},{"pid":"c5c6a1fb0e23a46963cc8b33f8085d00fb6cc0be","tid":1085027,"uid":55533,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T03:39:48.000Z","msg":"支那人就係癡線同弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n殲滅麻雀的結果使農田當中的害蟲幾乎沒有天敵，而讓次年的糧食嚴重欠收，發生極為嚴重的饑荒問題[2]。不久後，包括鄭作新在內的很多鳥類學者通過野外研究，證實了在麻雀的食譜中，人工種植的穀物僅占不到50%的比重，他們的研究成果甚至發表在中共中央機關報《人民日報》上，可謂史無前例。1959年11月27日，中國科學院黨組書記張勁夫，綜合生物學界的意見，寫了一份「關於麻雀問題向主席的報告」。隨即在1960年3月16日，毛澤東在為中央起草的關於衛生工作的指示中改變了消滅麻雀的決定，提出麻雀不打了，代之的是打臭蟲，4月19日，這一包含修正後「除四害」的《農業發展綱》四十條，正式提請第二屆全國人民代表大會第二次會議討論通過，向全國公佈。從「承受不起麻雀造成的糧食損失而轟麻雀」到「全面權衡利弊、寧可遭受糧食損失也要容忍麻雀」 ，最後還是肯定了麻雀的作用，改變了「轟麻雀」的做法。<br />\n<br />\n事後清算科學家 <br />\n編輯<br />\n在數年後開始的「文革」中，這些反對打麻雀運動的科學家被扣上「利用麻雀做文章」來反對毛主席、反對「大躍進」、反對「最高指示」等種種「罪名」，受到殘酷迫害。朱洗在1962年就已病逝，但此時仍被扣上把毛主席同腓特烈大帝相提並論、公開反對毛主席的罪狀，因此受到紅衛兵砸碑掘墳、曝其屍骨。"},{"pid":"aca19a9b31a64bebeec0f90f8bb6f721dd92f9ed","tid":1085027,"uid":28641,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T04:06:54.000Z","msg":"笑撚到仆街<br />\n講咁撚多都好<br />\n弦外之音又好<br />\n<br />\n屌<br />\n今日你咪又係唔會上街<br />\n一味無病呻吟係度叫春<br />\n抵你班支那香港人低賤民族做成支那人一生奴隸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd0aa9494443ad15688e11fff7bf3d90bfbc2d1","tid":1085027,"uid":177089,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"aca19a9b31a64bebeec0f90f8bb6f721dd92f9ed","tid":1085027,"uid":28641,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T04:06:54.000Z","msg":"笑撚到仆街<br />\n講咁撚多都好<br />\n弦外之音又好<br />\n<br />\n屌<br />\n今日你咪又係唔會上街<br />\n一味無病呻吟係度叫春<br />\n抵你班支那香港人低賤民族做成支那人一生奴隸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T04:12:11.000Z","msg":"我依家每次見到斑鳩都會行埋去踢鳩佢地<br />\n你呢？"}]}